- soak skewers for heat protecc

[ Tare ]
- Put all the Tare ingredients in a small saucepan and bring it to a boil 
  - Soy sauce (120g)
  - Mirin (40g)
  - Sugar (20g)
  - Sake (100g)
- Reduce the heat to simmer and cook for about 5 minutes until the quantity of tare is reduced by a third

[ Skewers ]
- chicken thigh / breast, chopped into 2.5cm cubes
- spring onion, cut into 3cm lengths
- baste chicken with tare, cook 3 mins
- flip and brush with tare, cook 3 mins
- flip again, baste again, cook 30s
